name: The Better Miss Scarlet
description:
I must say I am very happy I can upload this again. This was the first addition to the "The Better" series.

What inspired me to make this was how angry I got when I first saw the Miss Scarlet face. I can of course live with blurry Roblox faces. But this face took it to an extreme. The eyes weren't even symmetrical and the lips look as if a two year old tried putting on lipstick for the first time. 

Feel free to use this in any way you want. No credit to me is needed. I'm just happy that there is a better version of this face in existence.  

To compare this to the original: https://www.roblox.com/Miss-Scarlet-item?id=334656210
